<div id="banner">
	<h1>Learning on the Road</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Boston Globe: <a href="http://www.boston.com/dailyglobe2/048/nation/Road_scholar_finds_home_at_MIT .shtml">Road scholar finds home at MIT</a>. A fascinating story about a boy who learned while traveling the country with his father, and is now an assistant professor at MIT.</p>

<blockquote>He will explain, with a sweet smile, that our society is far too age- segregated: &#8221;It is my single passive political stance,&#8221; he said - and argues that a lot of other people could do what he does if they had the same encouragement.</blockquote>

<p><em>Amen to that!</em></p>

<p class="posted">posted March 05, 2002 04:02 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_education">Education</a>)  <a href="000175" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
